What's New In NVIDIA AI Enterprise.Hello, <br>
<br><br>
Here are product release highlights from the past few weeks in NVIDIA AI En=
terprise:
<br>
<ul>
<li>NVIDIA GPU Operator v25.10.0 Is Now Available
</li>
<li>The NVIDIA NeMo Data Designer Microservice Is Now Available
</li>
</ul>








<br>
<b>NVIDIA GPU Operator v25.10.0 Is Now Available
</b>
<br> <br>




The NVIDIA GPU Operator is a Kubernetes operator that simplifies the deploy=
ment and management of all NVIDIA software required to provision GPUs in a =
Kubernetes cluster. NVIDIA GPU Operator v25.10.0 is the first version that =
is =E2=80=9CGovernment Ready=E2=80=9D, making it available for regulated in=
dustries where STIG compliance and FIPS support are required.&nbsp;




<br><br>
The NVIDIA GPU Operator now uses distroless images to reduce security vulne=
rabilities and CDI by default in the Container Toolkit. This release also p=
rovides support for the latest Blackwell platforms: HGX B300 and GB300 NVL7=
2.
<br><br><br>




Resources:
<br>
<ul>
<li><a href=3D"https://catalog.ngc.nvidia.com/orgs/nvidia/containers/gpu-op=
erator?version=3Dv25.10.0" rel=3D"nofollow"><u>Get NVIDIA GPU Operator</u><=
/a></li>
<li><a href=3D"https://docs.nvidia.com/datacenter/cloud-native/gpu-operator=
/25.10/release-notes.html" rel=3D"nofollow"><u>NVIDIA GPU Operator 25.10.00=
 Release Notes</u></a></li>
<li><a href=3D"https://docs.nvidia.com/datacenter/cloud-native/gpu-operator=
/25.10/platform-support.html#gpu-operator-component-matrix" rel=3D"nofollow=
"><u>NVIDIA GPU Operator Component Matrix</u></a></li>




</ul>
<br><br>
















<b>The NVIDIA NeMo Data Designer Microservice Is Now Available
</b>
<br><br>
NVIDIA NeMo Microservices is a modular suite of tools for managing the AI a=
gent lifecycle. It includes software for data processing, model fine-tuning=
 and evaluation, reinforcement learning, policy enforcement, and system obs=
ervability.&nbsp;
<br><br>
The new NVIDIA NeMo Data Designer Microservice provides domain experts a wa=
y to generate high-quality, task-specific synthetic data at scale through p=
rompting or providing seed examples, configurable schemas and AI-powered ge=
neration models, for specializing enterprise AI agents.




<br><br><br>
Resources:
<br>
<ul>
<li><a href=3D"https://catalog.ngc.nvidia.com/orgs/nvidia/teams/nemo-micros=
ervices/containers/data-designer?version=3D25.10" rel=3D"nofollow"><u>Get t=
he NVIDIA NeMo Data Designer Microservice</u></a></li>
<li><a href=3D"https://docs.nvidia.com/nemo/microservices/latest/design-syn=
thetic-data-from-scratch-or-seeds/docker-compose.html" rel=3D"nofollow">
<u>Deploy NeMo Data Designer with Docker</u></a></li>
<li><a href=3D"https://docs.nvidia.com/nemo/microservices/index.html" rel=
=3D"nofollow"><u>NVIDIA NeMo Microservices Documentation</u></a></li>
</ul>
<br>
<br>
Best,
<br>
The NVIDIA NGC Team
