<b>NVIDIA GPU Operator v25.10.0 Is Now Available
</b>
<br> <br>




The NVIDIA GPU Operator is a Kubernetes operator that simplifies the deploy=
ment and management of all NVIDIA software required to provision GPUs in a =
Kubernetes cluster. NVIDIA GPU Operator v25.10.0 is the first version that =
is =E2=80=9CGovernment Ready=E2=80=9D, making it available for regulated in=
dustries where STIG compliance and FIPS support are required.&nbsp;




<br><br>
The NVIDIA GPU Operator now uses distroless images to reduce security vulne=
rabilities and CDI by default in the Container Toolkit. This release also p=
rovides support for the latest Blackwell platforms: HGX B300 and GB300 NVL7=
2.
